The `content` property of the `:after` selector can be used to separate list items:

```css
/* Inline items */
span:not(:last-child):after {
    content: ' â€¢ ';
}

/* List items */
li:not(:last-child):after {
    content: ',';
}
```

The footer of this website uses the same technique.

